/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.poster.avif?t=1741823854\" width=750 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.webm?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320520/extras/b35b289fa4af6e940dee7ddb5cc63ccf.mp4?t=1741823854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With the Q key, explore all the available pieces: movement blocks, directional blocks, portals, and level endings.</strong></p>",
